    <sys:String x:Key="LOCSsvFilePatternTooltip" xml:space="preserve">In addition, you can used:
- {DateModified}&#x09;&#x09;yyyy-MM-dd
- {DateTimeModified}&#x09;&#x09;yyyy-MM-dd HH_mm_ss
- {digit}&#x09;&#x09;&#x09;number(s)
    
Example:
GameName_20200107-1&#x09;=>&#x09;{Name}_{digit}-{digit}
GameName_2020-01-07&#x09;=>&#x09;{Name}_{DateModified}</sys:String>

    <sys:String x:Key="LOCSsvGlobalSearchTooltip" xml:space="preserve">Add this folder for all games.
    
